unavailable-subtitle: Not enough political support. [? if z_relation < 45: The Center Party does not support this. ?] [? if ddp_relation < 40: The Democrats are hesitant. ?] [? if nsdap_r >= 25: The NSDAP is too popular — no coalition will risk it. ?]
on-arrival: {!
    Q.nsdap_banned = 1;
    Q.ban_party_timer = 24;

    if (Q.nsdap_r >= 25 || Q.sa_strength > 400) {
        Q.nsdap_ban_violence = 3;
        Q.sa_strength *= 0.3;
        Q.sa_militancy += 0.5;
    } else if (Q.nsdap_r >= 15 || Q.sa_strength > 200) {
        Q.nsdap_ban_violence = 2;
        Q.sa_strength *= 0.2;
        Q.sa_militancy += 0.3;
    } else {
        Q.nsdap_ban_violence = 1;
        Q.sa_strength *= 0.1;
        Q.sa_militancy += 0.2;
    }

    Q.pro_republic += 5;
    Q.nationalism -= 10;

    if (Q.z_relation >= 45) Q.z_relation += 5;
    else Q.z_relation -= 10;

    Q.ddp_relation += 8;
    Q.dvp_relation -= 5;
    Q.kpd_relation += 10;

    if (Q.dnvp_line === 3) Q.dnvp_relation -= 20;

    Q.workers_dnvp += Q.workers_nsdap * 0.3;
    Q.workers_other += Q.workers_nsdap * 0.2;
    Q.workers_spd += Q.workers_nsdap * 0.1;
    Q.workers_nsdap *= 0.4;

    Q.old_middle_dnvp += Q.old_middle_nsdap * 0.4;
    Q.old_middle_dvp += Q.old_middle_nsdap * 0.2;
    Q.old_middle_other += Q.old_middle_nsdap * 0.1;
    Q.old_middle_nsdap *= 0.3;

    Q.new_middle_dnvp += Q.new_middle_nsdap * 0.3;
    Q.new_middle_dvp += Q.new_middle_nsdap * 0.2;
    Q.new_middle_ddp += Q.new_middle_nsdap * 0.15;
    Q.new_middle_nsdap *= 0.35;

    Q.rural_dnvp += Q.rural_nsdap * 0.4;
    Q.rural_other += Q.rural_nsdap * 0.2;
    Q.rural_nsdap *= 0.4;

    Q.unemployed_kpd += Q.unemployed_nsdap * 0.2;
    Q.unemployed_other += Q.unemployed_nsdap * 0.3;
    Q.unemployed_nsdap *= 0.5;

    Q.catholics_z += Q.catholics_nsdap * 0.3;
    Q.catholics_other += Q.catholics_nsdap * 0.2;
    Q.catholics_nsdap *= 0.5;
!}
go-to: nsdap_ban_civil_war if nsdap_ban_violence >= 3; nsdap_ban_unrest if nsdap_ban_violence = 2; nsdap_ban_resistance if nsdap_ban_violence = 1

@nsdap_ban_civil_war
on-arrival: civil_war_seen = 1; in_civil_war = 1

**CIVIL WAR**

The banning of the NSDAP has triggered a massive violent response. SA units across Germany have risen in armed rebellion. The Reichswehr is mobilizing, but street battles rage in multiple cities.

- @civil_war: Continue...

@nsdap_ban_unrest
on-arrival: crisis_urgency += 2; sa_strength += 50; strife += 2

**Major Unrest**

The NSDAP ban has triggered widespread violence. SA paramilitaries have attacked government buildings, fought street battles with the Reichsbanner, and assassinated several prominent republicans. The SA has gone underground but remains dangerous.

- @root: Continue...

@nsdap_ban_resistance
on-arrival: sa_strength += 20; strife += 1

**Underground Resistance**

The NSDAP ban has been implemented with relative success. While SA cells operate underground and isolated acts of terrorism occur, the Nazi movement has been largely suppressed.

- @root: Continue...

@ban_dnvp_menu
on-arrival: {!
    // Only Hugenberg DNVP can be banned
    if (Q.dnvp_line === 1) {
        Q.can_ban_dnvp = 0;
    } else {
        Q.ban_support = Q.spd_normalized;

        if (Q.z_relation >= 50 && Q.dnvp_line === 3) {
            Q.ban_support += Q.z_normalized * 0.5;
        }
        if (Q.ddp_relation >= 45) {
            Q.ban_support += Q.ddp_normalized * 0.8;
        }
        if (Q.kpd_relation >= 50) {
            Q.ban_support += Q.kpd_normalized;
        }
        if (Q.sapd_formed && Q.sapd_relation >= 45) {
            Q.ban_support += Q.sapd_normalized * 0.6;
        }
        if (Q.csvd_flee && Q.kvp_relation >= 40) {
            Q.ban_support += Q.kvp_normalized * 0.5;
        }

        // DNVP must be on Hugenberg line and have crossed into anti-constitutional territory
        Q.ban_threshold = 0.52;
        if (Q.pro_republic < 65) Q.ban_threshold = 0.60;
        if (Q.dnvp_line !== 3) Q.ban_threshold += 0.15;

        Q.can_ban_dnvp = Q.ban_support >= Q.ban_threshold ? 1 : 0;
    }
!}
go-to: dnvp_cannot_ban if dnvp_line = 1; dnvp_ban_show if dnvp_line != 1

@dnvp_cannot_ban

**Banning the DNVP:**

Kuno von Westarp's DNVP operates within the constitutional order. The Constitutional Court would reject this case immediately — banning them would be a flagrant abuse of power.

- @ban_party_menu: Back

@dnvp_ban_show

